msgid "Rasterize (vector to raster)"
msgstr "Rasterizacija (vektor u raster)"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectorconversion.rst:307
msgid ""
"Converts vector geometries (points, lines and polygons) into a raster image."
msgstr ""
"Pretvara vektorske geometrije (tačke, linije i poligone) u rastersku sliku."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectorconversion.rst:312
msgid "**Default menu**: :menuselection:`Raster --> Conversion`"
msgstr "**Podrazumevani meni**: :menuselection:`Raster --> Pretvaranje`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectorconversion.rst:338
msgid ""
"Defines the attribute field from which the attributes for the pixels should "
"be chosen"
msgstr "Definiše atributsko polje iz koga se biraju atributi za piksele"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectorconversion.rst:347
msgid "A fixed value to burn into a band for all features."
msgstr "Fiksna vrednost koja se upisuje u kanal za sve objekte."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectorconversion.rst:348
msgid "**Burn value extracted from the \"Z\" values of the feature**"
msgstr "**Upisna vrednost izdvojena iz \"Z\" vrednosti objekta**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectorconversion.rst:349
msgid "``USE_Z``"
msgstr "``USE_Z``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectorconversion.rst:353
msgid ""
"Indicates that a burn value should be extracted from the \"Z\" values of the"
" feature. Works with points and lines (linear interpolation along each "
"segment). For polygons, works properly only if they are flat (same Z value "
"for all vertices)"
msgstr ""
"Označava da se upisna vrednost izdvaja iz \"Z\" vrednosti objekta. Radi sa "
"tačkama i linijama (linearna interpolacija duž svakog segmenta). Za poligone"
" radi ispravno samo ako su ravni (ista Z vrednost za sva temena)"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectorconversion.rst:356
msgid "**Output raster size units**"
msgstr "**Jedinice veličine izlaznog rastera**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectorconversion.rst:357
msgid "``UNITS``"
msgstr "``UNITS``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectorconversion.rst:358
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectorconversion.rst:450
msgid "[enumeration]"
msgstr "[nabrajanje]"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectorconversion.rst:360
msgid "Default: 0"
msgstr "Podrazumevano: 0"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectorconversion.rst:361
msgid "Units to use when defining the output raster size/resolution. One of:"
msgstr ""
"Jedinice koje se koriste pri definisanju veličine/rezolucije izlaznog "
"rastera. Jedno od:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectorconversion.rst:364
msgid "0 --- Pixels"
msgstr "0 --- Pikseli"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectorconversion.rst:365
msgid "1 --- Georeferenced units"
msgstr "1 --- Georeferencirane jedinice"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectorconversion.rst:367
msgid "**Width/Horizontal resolution**"
msgstr "**Širina/vodoravna rezolucija**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectorconversion.rst:368
msgid "``WIDTH``"
msgstr "``WIDTH``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectorconversion.rst:372
msgid ""
"Sets the width (if size units is \"Pixels\") or horizontal resolution (if "
"size units is \"Georeferenced units\") of the output raster. Minimum value: "
"0.0."
msgstr ""
"Postavlja širinu (ako su jedinice veličine \"Pikseli\") ili vodoravnu "
"rezoluciju (ako su jedinice veličine \"Georeferencirane jedinice\") izlaznog"
" rastera. Najmanja vrednost: 0.0."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectorconversion.rst:375
msgid "**Height/Vertical resolution**"
msgstr "**Visina/uspravna rezolucija**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectorconversion.rst:376
msgid "``HEIGHT``"
msgstr "``HEIGHT``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectorconversion.rst:380
msgid ""
"Sets the height (if size units is \"Pixels\") or vertical resolution (if "
"size units is \"Georeferenced units\") of the output raster."
msgstr ""
"Postavlja visinu (ako su jedinice veličine \"Pikseli\") ili uspravnu "
"rezoluciju (ako su jedinice veličine \"Georeferencirane jedinice\") izlaznog"
" rastera."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectorconversion.rst:383
msgid "**Output extent**"
msgstr "**Izlazni obuhvat**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectorconversion.rst:386
msgid "``EXTENT``"
msgstr "``EXTENT``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectorconversion.rst:387
msgid "[extent]"
msgstr "[obuhvat]"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectorconversion.rst:388
msgid ""
"Extent of the output raster layer. If the extent is not specified, the "
"minimum extent that covers the selected reference layer(s) will be used."
msgstr ""
"Obuhvat izlaznog rasterskog sloja. Ako se obuhvat ne zada, koristi se "
"najmanji obuhvat koji pokriva izabrane referentne slojeve."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/algs_include.rst:3
msgid "Available methods are:"
msgstr "Dostupni metodi su:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/algs_include.rst:5
msgid ""
"Calculate from layer…: uses extent of a layer loaded in the current project"
msgstr ""
"Izračunaj iz sloja…: koristi obuhvat sloja učitanog u tekućem projektu"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/algs_include.rst:6
msgid ""
"Calculate from layout map…: uses extent of a :ref:`layout map item "
"<layout_map_item>` in the active project"
msgstr ""
"Izračunaj iz karte rasporeda…: koristi obuhvat :ref:`stavke karte u "
"rasporedu <layout_map_item>` u aktivnom projektu"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/algs_include.rst:8
msgid ""
"Calculate from bookmark…: uses extent of a saved :ref:`bookmark "
"<sec_bookmarks>`"
msgstr ""
"Izračunaj iz obeleživača…: koristi obuhvat sačuvanog :ref:`obeleživača "
"<sec_bookmarks>`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/algs_include.rst:9
msgid "Use map canvas extent"
msgstr "Koristi obuhvat platna karte"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/algs_include.rst:10
msgid ""
"Draw on canvas: click and drag a rectangle delimiting the area to take into "
"account"
msgstr ""
"Nacrtaj na platnu: klikom i prevlačenjem nacrtajte pravougaonik koji "
"ograničava područje koje se uzima u obzir"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/algs_include.rst:11
msgid "Enter the coordinates as ``xmin, xmax, ymin, ymax``"
msgstr "Unesite koordinate kao ``xmin, xmax, ymin, ymax``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectorconversion.rst:396
msgid "**Assign a specified NoData value to output bands**"
msgstr "**Dodeli zadatu NoData vrednost izlaznim kanalima**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectorconversion.rst:399
msgid "``NODATA``"
msgstr "``NODATA``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectorconversion.rst:403
msgid "Assigns a specified NoData value to output bands"
msgstr "Dodeljuje zadatu NoData vrednost izlaznim kanalima"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectorconversion.rst:408
msgid "Default: ``[Save to temporary file]``"
msgstr "Podrazumevano: ``[Save to temporary file]``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectorconversion.rst:409
msgid ""
"Specification of the output raster layer. :ref:`One of "
"<output_parameter_widget>`:"
msgstr ""
"Specifikacija izlaznog rasterskog sloja. :ref:`Jedno od "
"<output_parameter_widget>`:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectorconversion.rst:416
msgid ""
"For ``Save to File``, the output format has to be specified. All GDAL raster"
" formats are supported. For ``Save to a Temporary File`` the QGIS default "
"raster format will be used."
msgstr ""
"Za ``Save to File`` mora se zadati izlazni format. Podržani su svi GDAL "
"rasterski formati. Za ``Save to a Temporary File`` koristi se podrazumevani "
"QGIS rasterski format."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectorconversion.rst:440
msgid ""
"For adding one or more creation options that control the raster to be "
"created (colors, block size, file compression...). For convenience, you can "
"rely on predefined profiles (see :ref:`GDAL driver options section "
"<gdal_createoptions>`)."
msgstr ""
"Za dodavanje jedne ili više opcija kreiranja koje upravljaju rasterom koji "
"se pravi (boje, veličina bloka, kompresija datoteke...). Radi praktičnosti "
"možete se osloniti na unapred definisane profile (pogledajte :ref:`odeljak o"
" opcijama GDAL drajvera <gdal_createoptions>`)."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectorconversion.rst:446
msgid ""
"Batch Process and Model Designer: separate multiple options with a pipe "
"character (``|``)."
msgstr ""
"Grupna obrada i Dizajner modela: više opcija razdvojite uspravnom crtom "
"(``|``)."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectorconversion.rst:448
msgid "**Output data type**"
msgstr "**Tip izlaznih podataka**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectorconversion.rst:449
msgid "``DATA_TYPE``"
msgstr "``DATA_TYPE``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectorconversion.rst:452
msgid "Default: 5"
msgstr "Podrazumevano: 5"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectorconversion.rst:453
msgid "Defines the format of the output raster file."
msgstr "Definiše format izlazne rasterske datoteke."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectorconversion.rst:455
msgid "Options:"
msgstr "Opcije:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/algs_include.rst:9
msgid "0 --- Byte        (Eight bit unsigned integer (quint8))"
msgstr "0 --- Byte        (Osmobitni ceo broj bez znaka (quint8))"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/algs_include.rst:10
msgid "1 --- Int16       (Sixteen bit signed integer (qint16))"
msgstr "1 --- Int16       (Šesnaestobitni ceo broj sa znakom (qint16))"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/algs_include.rst:11
msgid "2 --- UInt16      (Sixteen bit unsigned integer (quint16))"
msgstr "2 --- UInt16      (Šesnaestobitni ceo broj bez znaka (quint16))"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/algs_include.rst:12
msgid "3 --- UInt32      (Thirty two bit unsigned integer (quint32))"
msgstr "3 --- UInt32      (Tridesetdvobitni ceo broj bez znaka (quint32))"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/algs_include.rst:13
msgid "4 --- Int32       (Thirty two bit signed integer (qint32))"
msgstr "4 --- Int32       (Tridesetdvobitni ceo broj sa znakom (qint32))"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/algs_include.rst:14
msgid "5 --- Float32     (Thirty two bit floating point (float))"
msgstr "5 --- Float32     (Tridesetdvobitni broj u pokretnom zarezu (float))"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/algs_include.rst:15
msgid "6 --- Float64     (Sixty four bit floating point (double))"
msgstr ""
"6 --- Float64     (Šezdesetčetvorobitni broj u pokretnom zarezu (double))"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/algs_include.rst:16
msgid "7 --- CInt16      (Complex Int16)"
msgstr "7 --- CInt16      (Kompleksni Int16)"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/algs_include.rst:17
msgid "8 --- CInt32      (Complex Int32)"
msgstr "8 --- CInt32      (Kompleksni Int32)"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/algs_include.rst:18
msgid "9 --- CFloat32    (Complex Float32)"
msgstr "9 --- CFloat32    (Kompleksni Float32)"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/algs_include.rst:19
msgid "10 --- CFloat64   (Complex Float64)"
msgstr "10 --- CFloat64   (Kompleksni Float64)"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/algs_include.rst:20
msgid "11 --- Int8       (Eight bit signed integer (qint8))"
msgstr "11 --- Int8       (Osmobitni ceo broj sa znakom (qint8))"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/algs_include.rst:22
msgid ""
"Available options depend on the GDAL version built with QGIS (see "
":menuselection:`Help --> About` menu)"
msgstr ""
"Dostupne opcije zavise od GDAL verzije sa kojom je QGIS izgrađen (pogledajte"
" meni :menuselection:`Pomoć --> O programu`)"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectorconversion.rst:461
msgid "**Pre-initialize the output image with value**"
msgstr "**Prethodno inicijalizuj izlaznu sliku vrednošću**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectorconversion.rst:464
msgid "``INIT``"
msgstr "``INIT``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectorconversion.rst:466
msgid ""
"Pre-initializes the output image bands with this value. Not marked as the "
"NoData value in the output file. The same value is used in all the bands."
msgstr ""
"Prethodno inicijalizuje kanale izlazne slike ovom vrednošću. Ne označava se "
"kao NoData vrednost u izlaznoj datoteci. Ista vrednost koristi se u svim "
"kanalima."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectorconversion.rst:469
msgid "**Invert rasterization**"
msgstr "**Obrni rasterizaciju**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectorconversion.rst:470
msgid "``INVERT``"
msgstr "``INVERT``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectorconversion.rst:474
msgid ""
"Burns the fixed burn value, or the burn value associated with the first "
"feature into all parts of the image not inside the provided polygon."
msgstr ""
"Upisuje fiksnu upisnu vrednost, ili upisnu vrednost pridruženu prvom "
"objektu, u sve delove slike koji nisu unutar zadatog poligona."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectorconversion.rst:501
msgid "Output raster layer"
msgstr "Izlazni rasterski sloj"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectorconversion.rst:506
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``gdal:rasterize``"
msgstr "**ID algoritma**: ``gdal:rasterize``"
